trick?<br><br>thanks in advance.<br><br>PS: I'm doing flux staff, tishan's kilt, acumen mask, mystic cloak. if anyone has any specific tips for either quest feel free to post <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/9/01 1:29:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> 1) what's the spawn time on the priest of najena in Unrest? I heard up to 1 hour <br><br>-=-=-=-=-=-=-=<br><br>The spawn for the place holder is about 45 - 50 minutes.  Wether or not the Priest spawns is random...<br><br>As for your faction - good luck friend  :) <p><P></P><P>-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=</P><P>Gder of Mithanial Marr</P><P>aka</P><P>Master of his domain</P><P>aka</P><P>gder@gder.net</P></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=thebends>TheBends</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/9/01 2:36:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> so uhm.....what's that &quot;good luck&quot; mean? :P won't wolf form work? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugder.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/9/01 3:07:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> It probably will, but don't quote me on that.<br><br>I was just thinking about having to go into Felwythe as a inky  :)<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarrik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arrik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/9/01 3:36:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> I am also an agnostic DE Wizard, but I am not KOS in Erudin. You can buy from most merchants, but you will be dubious to the caster guilds, and KOS to a few parties (Paladin and Cleric guilds, etc.) You *will* be KOS to Parlone in Erudin however. (I almost made the mistake of running up to the Mage guild but luckily I stopped to con her.) I don't know the best way to give her the final item. I think an Enchanter may need to charm her, but I would suspect the guards would all attack at that point. If that happened, I guess you could have a Druid or Wizard casting an Evac when the charm hit, and still have a window of a few seconds to hand in the item or something... Who knows?  There may be a way to sneak by in elemental form, since I don't think you can cast Wolf form in the Palace. I don't know if the elemental form works, it's just an idea, I don't have a ball of clay to test it.<br><br>You will be KOS in Felwithe, and probably KOS to all of the Parlones, I think they fall under KeepersOfTheArt faction or something, and it seems to be directly opposed to TheDead, or some other Dark Elf faction. (I think the Necromancers/ShadowKnights are under TheDead.)<br><br>The spawn time for the Ghoul placeholder is about 55 minutes I hear. People that I know personally have gotten the key in around 6 hours, as long as 12 hours or more, some as quick as 1.<br><br>I have not done this quest myself, I think I will just get a Runescale Cloak and skip the Mystic Cloak personally. I don't know of any Dark Elves that have a Mystic Cloak, if I see one I will certainly ask how they got it!<br><br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarrik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arrik</A> at: 2/9/01 3:40:06 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=thebends>TheBends</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/9/01 5:36:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> thanks for the info.<br><br>ah well I guess I'll skip that quest. Especially the almost 1 hour camp for the priest is really lame....of course, one could kamikaze it and go invis, then quickly turn in the items and eat the death...but nah, that camp sucks.<br><br>good to hear that I'm not kos in Erudin though, this will allow me to buy the 39 DD with no probs. Just gotta watch out for those holy jerks :P <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=thebends>TheBends</A> at: 2/9/01 5:38:27 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarrik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arrik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/11/01 1:20:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> I was dubious to all of the caster guilds unfortunately.  The only things I can buy in Erudin are normal supplies and to bank.  You may want to confirm this, but just stay away from the Gatecallers (Mages) because it is very easy to run up that flight of stairs and aggro Parlone.<br><br>Not being KOS in Erudin was good at level 20 because the Tox forest teleport become my most useful one.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Running to Overthere from levels 16-19 just for food (from Ill Omen) is just not fun. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Too risky.<br><br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umaultar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maultar</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/22/01 11:28:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> The quests area mensions that you need to go to cazic thule and get 3 clay balls so you can turn into an earth elemental to get into felwithe or whatever.  You still need to watch out for guards though.  Read the spoiler for mystic cloak. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utehutibloodstorm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tehuti Bloodstorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/15/01 2:20:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.toddalan.com/~berglund/ikp_hao.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dark Elf needs a little help with Mystic Cloak</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I was dubious to all of the caster guilds unfortunately. The only things I can buy in Erudin are normal supplies and to bank. You may want to confirm this, but just stay away from the Gatecallers (Mages) because it is very easy to run up that flight of stairs and aggro Parlone.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>I was considering this quest, but heard the balls of clay are a rare drop. And since no one hunts in Cazic anymore doesn't seem likely to be gotten.<br><br>Just an fyi Parlone is in the Enchanter guild second floor. Not 